{"tid":1688692,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 反抗 原來只係一句口號","createTime":"2019-11-02T13:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T14:34:37.000Z","uid":220787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc4a30f6067ce0b279a206c8599884bf7dbb766d","tid":1688692,"uid":220787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:57:51.000Z","msg":"發夢睇到5點幾一大批人一早散水<br />\n一邊行去ifc走<br />\n一邊嗌香港人 反抗<br />\n成件事真係好諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係想分化<br />\n但今日搭巴士出黎真係少人左好多 無人排長龍 無一車車黑衫<br />\n可能大家覺得講完好嬲 轉個頭就可以繼續吃喝玩樂<br />\n望住一個個手足被捕 真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果未有對策真係暫時唔好再港島比人一次過捉幾百人喇<br />\n香港人 反抗 唔係一句口號黎<br />\n係要做出黎架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"25699d9e5018c2152878c0bf0ffb0fb6048ecc66","tid":1688692,"uid":286564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武裝起義革命是刻不容緩<br />\n本人相信殺光這班黑警<br />\n香港便會回服太平<br />\n什麽魔法只是螢燭之光<br />\n毫無用處<br />\n一定要有必死的決心<br />\n只要有百多人每人手持火水、電油、天拿水，包圍黑警<br />\n哪怕不能除惡務盡嗎？<br />\n我們再不能心慈手軟<br />\n醒覺啦</span></strong>"}]}